, play an essential role in the rapidly growing e-beam market, and work closely with TSMC and major semiconductor fabs. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] With 14 customer support sites, two factories, and three R&D centers, our US locations service Intel and other customers and contribute to our holistic product portfolio."]], ["div", ["[->div<-] We saved your job [->div<-] How ASML is applying AI-native engineering for the next technology era\u00a0 [->div<-] Layer by layer, chip by chip, wafer by wafer, computational lithography is enabling chipmakers to push microchip technology to new limits [->div<-] Our Germany locations, such as Berlin and Dresden, specialize in optical manufacturing technology, precision manufacturing, as well as software development and customer support."]], ["tr", ["[->tr<-] "]], ["td", ["[->td<-] "]], ["th", ["[->th<-] "]], ["font", ["[->font<-] "]], ["li", ["[->li<-] "]], ["small", ["[->small<-] "]], ["strong", ["[->strong<-] "]], ["h1", ["[->h1<-] Changing the world, one nanometer at a time"]], ["h2", ["[->h2<-] Search [->h2<-] Discover computational lithography [->h2<-] Enable third party cookies to play this video [->h2<-] 60 locations, endless job opportunities [->h2<-] Learn [->h2<-] Work At ASML [->h2<-] Invest [->h2<-] Get in touch"]], ["h3", ["[->h3<-] Quick Links [->h3<-] Chinese mainland [->h3<-] Germany [->h3<-] Japan [->h3<-] The Netherlands [->h3<-] South Korea [->h3<-] Taiwan [->h3<-] United States"]], ["h4", ["[->h4<-] Social Media"]], ["h5", ["[->h5<-] "]], ["h6", ["[->h6<-] "]], ["span", ["[->span<-] 01 / 31 [->span<-] We're powering technology forward [->span<-] The machines behind the machines [->span<-] Our 2025 Annual Report [->span<-] Explore the highlights [->span<-] Learn more [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Enable third party cookies to play this video [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] What's it like to be on the ASML team? [->span<-] Search for your future job [->span<-] Latest Press Rel