[->b<-] "]], ["em", ["[->em<-] "]]], [["p", ["[->p<-] Saved jobs [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Find out more about ASML and link to information on our technology, products, and how we operate [->p<-] ASML is an innovation leader in the semiconductor industry. Find out what we do and why we do it. [->p<-] We\u2019re committed to independence, accountability and transparency, building a relationship of trust with our stakeholders. [->p<-] Find out what sustainability means to us at ASML and what concrete actions we are taking together with our customers, suppliers and partners. [->p<-] At ASML, we support our local communities through education, sports, arts and music, and other outreach activities. [->p<-] View key highlights, facts and figures, and more"]], ["div", ["[->div<-] We saved your job [->div<-] Learn about the technology behind our lithography, metrology and inspection, and software solutions. [->div<-] Find out how we provide our customers with the hardware, software and services they need to mass produce patterns on silicon. [->div<-] Explore careers at ASML and join the high-tech semiconductor industry, where you can work on technology that can change the world."]], ["tr", ["[->tr<-] "]], ["td", ["[->td<-] "]], ["th", ["[->th<-] "]], ["font", ["[->font<-] "]], ["li", ["[->li<-] "]], ["small", ["[->small<-] "]], ["strong", ["[->strong<-] "]], ["h1", ["[->h1<-] Inside a semiconductor industry leader"]], ["h2", ["[->h2<-] Search [->h2<-] Related content [->h2<-] Learn [->h2<-] Work At ASML [->h2<-] Invest [->h2<-] Get in touch"]], ["h3", ["[->h3<-] We provide chipmakers with everything they need \u2013 hardware, software and services \u2013 to mass produce patterns on silicon through lithography. [->h3<-] Technology [->h3<-] Products [->h3<-] Careers"]], ["h4", ["[->h4<-] Social Media"]], ["h5", ["[->h5<-] "]], ["h6", ["[->h6<-] "]], ["span", ["[->span<-] 01 / 21 [->span<-] About ASML [->span<-] Governance [->span<-] Sustainability [->span<-] Community engagement [->span<-] ASML at a glance [->span<-] Latest Press Releases [->span<-] May 16, 2026 [->span<-] \u00a0 [->span<-] Tata Electronics and ASML Announce Strategic Partnership to Advance the Semiconductor Manufacturing Ecosystem in India [->span<-] May 5, 2026 [->span<-] \u00a0 [->span<-] ASML CEO Christophe Fouquet co-signed opinion piece with European technology companies [->span<-] April 22, 2026 [->span<-] \u00a0 [->span<-] ASML discloses 2026 AGM results [->span<-] / [->span<-] Manage cookie settings [->span<-] Copyright \u00a9 2019-2026 (ASML) All Rights Reserved"]], ["b", ["[->b<-] "]], ["em", ["[->em<-] "]]], [["p", ["[->p<-] Saved jobs [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Unlocking the potential of semiconductor technology [->p<-] We enable groundbreaking technology to solve some of society's toughest challenges. Together with our partners, we provide leading patterning solutions that drive the advancement of microchips. [->p<-] Beijing [->p<-] Berlin, Germany [->p<-] Chandler, AZ, US [->p<-] Hillsboro, OR, US [->p<-] Hsinchu [->p<-] Hwasung, South Korea [->p<-] Linkou [->p<-] San Diego, CA, US [->p<-] Shanghai [->p<-] Shenzhen [->p<-] Silicon Valley, CA, US [->p<-] Tainan [->p<-] Tokyo, Japan [->p<-] Veldhoven, the Netherlands [->p<-] Wilton, CT, US [->p<-] Our research and manufacturing center for a range of modules for our e-beam inspection systems, as well as home to customer support for local chipmakers. [->p<-] A major R&D and manufacturing site with expertise in optics and wafer chuck technology. Produces key lithography components, including wafer tables and clamps, reticle chucks and mirror blocks. [->p<-] Home to our US Global Support Center for customers, our Chandler office houses employees from Customer Support, Sales, and other support departments. [->p<-] Our largest US customer support site, responsible for delivering the highest level of service throughout the life cycle of a lithography system. It\u2019s also the main training hub for customer support engineers in the US. [->p<-] Our Taiwanese headquarters, based in the Hsinchu Science Park, is home to local corporate functions as well as customer support and software development. [->p<-] Our headquarters in South Korea houses the ASML Korea Training Center for our customer support engineers supporting high-volume production at customer sites. It\u2019s also home to the Korea Repair Center for system parts. [->p<-] Our largest site in Asia, where we build reticle handlers for our lithography systems and YieldStar metrology systems, as well as refurbish mature systems. It's also home to our Asian Global Support Center for customers. [->p<-] The epicenter for the development and manufacturing of DUV and EUV light sources for lithography systems. It's also the main office of Cymer, an independently operated business within ASML. [->p<-] Our Chinese headquarters, housing customer support services and logistics, as well as corporate functions for our operations in China. It\u2019s also home to an R&D team focused on software development. [->p<-] The biggest ASML R&D center for software in Asia, working on a range of products and solutions, from process analyses, mathematical modeling, cloud computing, machine learning and big data. [->p<-] Our software and R&D powerhouse, specializing in computational applications to help chipmakers achieve higher manufacturing yields, as well as in e-beam metrology technology. [->p<-] Our main e-beam technology site, focused on R&D as well as the production of our e-beam inspection systems and solutions. [->p<-] Our Japanese headquarters, housing software development as well as customer support, logistics and local corporate functions. [->p<-] Our global headquarters is our biggest R&D and manufacturing site. It houses our European ASML Global Support Center, the Board of Management, and global corporate functions such as Legal and Investor Relations. [->p<-] Our largest US office and second-largest R&D center in ASML, with expertise in mechatronics, alignment and sensor technology and world-class optical R&D and manufacturing abilities. [->p<-] Year founded [->p<-] Total employees (FTEs) [->p<-] Nationalities [->p<-] Locations [->p<-] 2025 annual figures [->p<-] With over 60 locations worldwide, we are a growing global force in the semiconductor industry. [->p<-] Read about who we are, what guides us, and how we strive to make the world better for future generations. [->p<-] R&D, manufacturing and customer support are the pillars of ASML\u2019s organizational structure, supported by our corporate functions. [->p<-] From a leaky wooden shed to a global force, ASML's journey in the semiconductor industry began in 1984. [->p<-] Three continents, over 60 locations. Find out more about what it\u2019s like working at a world leader in the semiconductor industry. [->p<-] There are more than 44,000 ASML employees on payroll and flexible contracts, spread across offices in more than 60 locations worldwide. The company\u2019s headquarters, located in Veldhoven, the Netherlands, comprises over half of all employees. [->p<-] Contact us via the contact form and we'll get back to you as soon as possible"]], ["div", ["[->div<-] We saved your job [->div<-] > [->div<-] , [->div<-] > [->div<-] Find out what sustainability means to us at ASML and what concrete actions we are taking together with our customers, suppliers and partners. [->div<-] R&D, manufacturing, and customer support are the pillars of our organization, supported by our corporate functions. [->div<-] Innovation is never a straight line. But we know that even the biggest challenge can be overcome by chipping away at it, if necessary with hundreds of people over many years. [->div<-] Our stories help bring ASML to life. Let our people and technology inspire you, and read about what we\u2019re doing in our communities."]], ["tr", ["[->tr<-] "]], ["td", ["[->td<-] "]], ["th", ["[->th<-] "]], ["font", ["[->font<-] "]], ["li", ["[->li<-] "]], ["small", ["[->small<-] "]], ["strong", ["[->strong<-] "]], ["h1", ["[->h1<-] About ASML"]], ["h2", ["[->h2<-] Search [->h2<-] Learn [->h2<-] Work At ASML [->h2<-] Invest [->h2<-] Get in touch"]], ["h3", ["[->h3<-] Vision & mission [->h3<-] Beijing [->h3<-] Berlin, Germany [->h3<-] Chandler, AZ, US [->h3<-] Hillsboro, OR, US [->h3<-] Hsinchu [->h3<-] Hwasung, South Korea [->h3<-] Linkou [->h3<-] San Diego, CA, US [->h3<-] Shanghai [->h3<-] Shenzhen [->h3<-] Silicon Valley, CA, US [->h3<-] Tainan [->h3<-] Tokyo, Japan [->h3<-] Veldhoven, the Netherlands [->h3<-] Wilton, CT, US [->h3<-] Facts & figures [->h3<-] More about ASML [->h3<-] Organization [->h3<-] How we innovate [->h3<-] Stories"]], ["h4", ["[->h4<-] \u00a0ASML is an innovation leader in the semiconductor industry. We design and manufacture the lithography machines that are an essential part of chip manufacturing. [->h4<-] \u00a0 [->h4<-] We provide chipmakers with the hardware, software and services they need to mass produce microchips. Our advanced lithography systems use light to print the tiny patterns that form the circuits inside modern chips. [->h4<-] Social Media"]], ["h5", ["[->h5<-] We believe that technology can be a force for good in the world."]], ["h6", ["[->h6<-] "]], ["span", ["[->span<-] 01 / 34 [->span<-] More about our vision and mission [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->s