illiker, Mechanical Engineering Group Lead [->h3<-] Meet Mike Mercer, Optical Technician [->h3<-] Meet Piyush Savlani, Electrical Engineering Group Lead [->h3<-] Meet Ricardo Duran-Rodriguez, Software Engineer [->h3<-] Meet Shubhangi Alande, Software Engineer [->h3<-] Meet Yu Gong, Senior Optical Sensing Engineer [->h3<-] Compensation & benefits in the US [->h3<-] Growing your career at ASML [->h3<-] Career events in the US [->h3<-] Organization [->h3<-] History"]], ["h4", ["[->h4<-] With R&D and manufacturing centers on the West and East Coasts, and offices near all our local customers such as Intel, the United States plays an integral part in helping to advance ASML\u2019s holistic lithography product portfolio. [->h4<-] Explore our technology in the US [->h4<-] Social Media"]], ["h5", ["[->h5<-] Explore our job opportunities by category, ranging from data science to mechatronics and everything in between. [->h5<-] At ASML, career development is part of our culture. From technical training to leadership programs, we offer opportunities for growth at every stage. Discover how our colleagues are shaping their careers. \u00a0"]], ["h6", ["[->h6<-] Matt Ramey, San Diego, CA \u00a0\u00a0 [->h6<-] \u00a0 [->h6<-] Anagnostis Tsiatmas, Silicon Valley, CA \u00a0 \u00a0 [->h6<-] \u00a0 [->h6<-] Joyce Cornelis, Hillsboro, OR \u00a0\u00a0 [->h6<-] \u00a0 [->h6<-] Theo Parge, Wilton, CT [->h6<-] \u00a0"]], ["span", ["[->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Software & computer science [->span<-] Mechanical engineering [->span<-] Electrical engineering [->span<-] Optics [->span<-] Physics [->span<-] Electron optics [->span<-] Manufacturing [->span<-] Logistics and supply chain management [->span<-] Customer support [->span<-] Our employee-led networks and clubs foster a supportive environment and enhance a sense of belonging in our workplace. [->span<-] LGBTIQ+ [->span<-] Culture & nationality [->span<-] Women [->span<-] Neurodiversity [->span<-] Sustainability [->span<-] Military veterans [->span<-] Early career [->span<-] Parents [->span<-] Diversity & inclusion at ASML [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Transparency In Coverage [->span<-] Where can I locate ASML\u2019s Transparency in Coverage machine-readable files? [->span<-] Here, you\u2019ll find the\u00a0 [->span<-] \u00a0that are made available in response to the US federal Transparency in Coverage Rule. They include negotiated service rates and out-of-network allowed amounts between health plans and healthcare providers. The machine-readable files are formatted to allow researchers, regulators and application developers to more easily access and analyze data. The files accessible through this link are several terabytes in size, meaning that most personal computers won\u2019t be able to download them. [->span<-] Read Matt's story [->span<-] Read Anagnostis's story [->span<-] Read Joyce's story [->span<-] Read Theo's story [->span<-] Related content [->span<-] / [->span<-] / [->span<-] / [->span<-] Manage cookie settings [->span<-] Copyright \u00a9 2019-2026 (ASML) All Rights Reserved"]], ["b", ["[->b<-] "]], ["em", ["[->em<-] "]]], [["p", ["[->p<-] Saved jobs [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Home to our largest site in Asia, Taiwan plays a major role in the world\u2019s semiconductor industry and at ASML [->p<-] \u00a0 [->p<-] Employees [->p<-] Sites [->p<-] Nationalities [->p<-] Year established [->p<-] Field application engineer [->p<-] Find your passion at ASML Taiwan [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] In Linkou, we refurbish \u2018classic\u2019 PAS 5500 and TWINSCAN lithography systems for a new life and a new purpose. We also manufacture reticle handlers for our DUV lithography systems and maintain an EUV collector cleaning center to support our customers\u2019 needs. See open manufacturing jobs in Taiwan. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] Over 1,600 of our customer support engineers are based in Taiwan, mainly servicing TSMC, the world\u2019s third-largest chipmaker and our customer of more than 30 years. Most of our employees are centralized in Hsinchu, Taichung and Tainan, our major hubs on the island. Want to join the action? See all open customer support jobs in Taiwan. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] Our R&D in Taiwan is mainly focused on the following areas: module redesign, components design and software design for e-beam inspection and YieldStar optical metrology, where our engineers concentrate on getting our machines to \u2018talk to each other\u2019 in our customers\u2019 fabs. See all open R&D jobs in Taiwan. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] At our EUV and DUV lithography training centers in Taiwan, we prepare both our engineers and those of our customers, making sure they have the right skills, processes and knowledge to troubleshoot and maintain our products. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] Professionals from fields as diverse as human resources, finance, facility management and IT enable the company to run smoothly. See all open corporate functions jobs in Taiwan. [->p<-] Our engineers regularly collaborate with our global customers, including TSMC, to install, develop and maintain their systems. This gives our teams the best of both worlds \u2013 experience working with our world-leading lithography machines and the opportunity to learn from and work with the semiconductor industry\u2019s top players. [->p<-] When we set up the YieldStar optical metrology production line and teamed up with leading e-beam metrology and inspection tools supplier Hermes Microvision (HMI) in 2016, this cemented Taiwan\u2019s strategic position within ASML to deliver our holistic lithography solutions to our global customers. [->p<-] life at asml [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] Learn how we will support you to foster your own well-being and work-life balance, through courses, great working environment, flexibility and more. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] Being part of ASML means being part of something bigger that yourself. Discover the many ways you'll be able to volunteer, give back to your community and make a difference. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] Are you interested in sustainability? A keen sportsperson? Passionate - like us - about diversity and inclusion? Find out about our network and clubs for ASML employees. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] Did you know that we annually host one of the largest developer events in the world? From holiday-inspired occasions to community and industry events, there\u2019s always another occasion on our calendar that you can join. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] Consider your career path a playground. We have various tools in place to support you in driving your own development, from classroom training to personal coaching, potential acceleration programs and more. Learn how, with ASML, you\u2019ll have the time, opportunity, and support to drive your own development. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] We want you to join ASML to be part of progress. And we want you to stay because you share in our success. We offer highly competitive compensation and benefits packages to attract and retain the very best talent, which means your package will cover much more than just a salary. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] In Linkou, we refurbish \u2018classic\u2019 PAS 5500 and TWINSCAN lithography systems for a new life and a new purpose. These systems are shipped to customers around the world, who in turn use them in to make products such as LED, flat panels or MEMs, the chips that know which way is \u2018up\u2019. In our factory, engineers in blue cleanroom suits take apart machines and clean, repair and tweak them to ensure that they perform to their original specifications. [->p<-] Our YieldStar optical metrology solutions can quickly and accurately measure the quality of patterns on the wafer. Our HMI e-beam solutions help to locate and analyze individual chip defects amid millions of printed patterns. Delivering speed and accuracy, our metrology and inspection portfolio covers every step manufacturing processes, from R&D to mass production. [->p<-] Even though ASML is technically a hardware company, we have one of the world\u2019s largest and most pioneering software communities. As chips continue to drastically decrease in size, it would be impossible for our systems to manufacture at dimensions of 10nm or smaller without the software developed by ASML. As a result, our lithography systems are now a hybrid of high-tech hardware and advanced software. Our development teams work across a range of coding practices, providing innovative solutions to the intricate problems that affect the chip-making systems at the heart of the electronics industry. [->p<-] Fill in the form below to get in touch with the ASML recruitment department for Taiwan. We\u2019ll get back to you as soon as possible! [->p<-] Your privacy matters to ASML and we comply with applicable data protection laws. Please read the\u00a0 [->p<-] \u00a0carefully before submitting this form."]], ["div", ["[->div<-] We saved your job [->div<-] , [->div<-] + [->div<-] ( [->div<-] Optional [->div<-] ) [->div<-] Learn about the technology behind our lithography, metrology and inspection, and software solutions. [->div<-] Learn more about ASML at our campus events and exhibitions in Taiwan. [->div<-] With over 60 locations worldwide, we are a growing global force in the semiconductor industry."]], ["tr", ["[->tr<-] "]], ["td", ["[->td<-] "]], ["th", ["[->th<-] "]], ["font", ["[->font<-] "]], ["li", ["[->li<-] Competitive salary [->li<-] 13th and 14th month payment [->li<-] Competitive overtime and shift allowance [->li<-] Paid vacation and other time off [->li<-] Performance-based variable pay plan [->li<-] Long-term incentive plan [->li<-] Employee share purchase plan [->li<-] Health Insurance and health checks [->li<-] Labor insurance and group insurance (100% paid) [->li<-] Anniversary award [->li<-] Training and development opportunities, including educational assistance through our Global Training and Studies program and international job rotation opportunities [->li<-] Comprehensive welfare benefits package (free lunch, gym, yoga class\u2026)"]], ["small", ["[->small<-] "]], ["strong", ["[->strong<-] "]], ["h1", ["[->h1<-] Working in Taiwan"]], ["h2", ["[->h2<-] Search [->h2<-] Learn [->h2<-] Work At ASML [->h2<-] Invest [->h2<-] Get in touch"]], ["h3", ["[->h3<-] Taiwan at a glance [->h3<-] Our technology in Taiwan [->h3<-] Refurbished systems [->h3<-] YieldStar optical metrology and e-beam inspection [->h3<-] Software [->h3<-] Technology [->h3<-] Career events in Taiwan [->h3<-] ASML at a glance"]], ["h4", ["[->h4<-] Our multinational teams are based in Hsinchu, Linkou, Taichung, Tainan and Kaohsiung. With a core focus on manufacturing and customer support, our engineers benefit from exclusive access to our industry-leading machines and customers, including TSMC. [->h4<-] ASML is an established force in Taiwan with four customer support offices, DUV and EUV training centers and two production plants. [->h4<-] Employee benefits [->h4<-] In Taiwan, we work on refurbishing our more mature lithography systems, and we also develop e-beam metrology and inspection systems, and the software that\u2019s crucial to manufacturing the latest-generation chips. [->h4<-] Read our most frequently asked questions about applying for a job at ASML in Taiwan. [->h4<-] Contact us [->h4<-] Social Media"]], ["h5", ["[->h5<-] "]], ["h6", ["[->h6<-] "]], ["span", ["[->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->s