holiday-inspired occasions to community and industry events, there\u2019s always another occasion on our calendar that you can join. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] Consider your career path a playground. We have various tools in place to support you in driving your own development, from classroom training to personal coaching, potential acceleration programs and more. Learn how, with ASML, you\u2019ll have the time, opportunity, and support to drive your own development. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] We want you to join ASML to be part of progress. And we want you to stay because you share in our success. We offer highly competitive compensation and benefits packages to attract and retain the very best talent, which means your package will cover much more than just a salary. [->p<-] Japan\u2019s history of semiconductors goes back to the beginnings of the industry in the 1950s. Today, the country boasts more than 30 companies with fabs. [->p<-] At ASML Japan, we deliver on our commitments to both customers and employees. The international culture that combines a Dutch company with Japanese employees creates a dynamic, engaging environment in which to work. [->p<-] Our core focus in Japan is customer support. Our engineers enjoy an international environment and work closely with a range of high-tech companies, including Kioxia (formerly Toshiba Memory), Sony and Micron. Our Japan headquarters are in Tokyo, but we also have offices in Hiroshima, Kumamoto, Nagasaki, Tsuruoka Yokkaichi and Kitakami. [->p<-] Read our  [->p<-] Fill in the form below to get in touch with the ASML recruitment department for Japan. We\u2019ll get back to you as soon as possible! [->p<-] Your privacy matters to ASML and we comply with applicable data protection laws. Please read the\u00a0 [->p<-] \u00a0carefully before submitting this form."]], ["div", ["[->div<-] We saved your job [->div<-] + [->div<-] + [->div<-] ( [->div<-] Optional [->div<-] ) [->div<-] With a strong focus on customer support and 