roduction process."]], ["h6", ["[->h6<-] "]], ["span", ["[->span<-] Figures - Germany [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] 0 [->span<-] 1 [->span<-] 2 [->span<-] 3 [->span<-] 4 [->span<-] 5 [->span<-] 6 [->span<-] 7 [->span<-] 8 [->span<-] 9 [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Enable third party cookies to view this form [->span<-] Below you can enable third party cookies. Your choice will be saved and the page will refresh. [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Your message [->span<-] Related content [->span<-] / [->span<-] / [->span<-] / [->span<-] Manage cookie settings [->span<-] Copyright \u00a9 2019-2026 (ASML) All Rights Reserved"]], ["b", ["[->b<-] "]], ["em", ["[->em<-] "]]], [["p", ["[->p<-] Saved jobs [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] \u00a0\u00a0Shaping the future of technology\u00a0 [->p<-] \u00a0\u00a0Tapping into our collective potential [->p<-] \u00a0\u00a0Innovation built on trust and respect [->p<-] Every day, our colleagues in R&D, manufacturing, customer support, and corporate functions take on the exciting challenge of building and maintaining the most advanced lithography systems in the world."]], ["div", ["[->div<-] We saved your job [->div<-] See our internships, scholarships, and career events for students and graduates in the Netherlands and the US. [->div<-] R&D, manufacturing, and customer support are the pillars of our organization, supported by our corporate functions. [->div<-] Find out what it\u2019s like working at a semiconductor industry leader. Discover job benefits, clubs and events, and our culture."]], ["tr", ["[->tr<-] "]], ["td", ["[->td<-] "]], ["th", ["[->th<-] "]], ["font", ["[->font<-] "]], ["li", ["[->li<-] "]], ["small", ["[->small<-] "]], ["strong", ["[->strong<-] ASML: a work environment like no other [->strong<-] \u2022 [->strong<-] \u2022 [->strong<-] \u2022"]], ["h1", ["[->h1<-] Technical fields"]], ["h2", ["[->h2<-] Search [->h2<-] Learn [->h2<-] Work At ASML [->h2<-] Invest [->h2<-] Get in touch"]], ["h3", ["[->h3<-] Technical fields [->h3<-] Students & new graduates [->h3<-] Organization [->h3<-] Working at ASML"]], ["h4", ["[->h4<-] Explore our job opportunities by tec [->h4<-] hnical fields, ranging from data science to mechatronics and everything in between. [->h4<-] Social Media"]], ["h5", ["[->h5<-] "]], ["h6", ["[->h6<-] "]], ["span", ["[->span<-] Read more [->span<-] \ufeff [->span<-] ASML is at the heart of progress in technology. Most of the electronic devices you use daily are only possible thanks to our lithography systems. [->span<-] Chemistry & materials science [->span<-] Discover the possibilities of chemistry and materials science jobs at ASML. [->span<-] Computer science & software engineering [->span<-] Find out what it's like working as a computer scientist or software developer at ASML working in C++, C#, Python or Java. [->span<-] Data science [->span<-] Discover how you can develop your data science career at ASML. [->span<-] Electrical engineering [->span<-] Work at the leading edge of electrical innovation. Explore the opportunities for electrical engineers at ASML. [->span<-] Logistics & supply chain management [->span<-] Discover jobs in supply chain management and logistics at ASML and start planning for your future. [->span<-] Mathematics [->span<-] Practice mathematics to the extreme. Discover all our opportunities in math at ASML. [->span<-] Mechanical engineering [->span<-] Design, build and test exceptionally high-performance systems as a mechanical engineer at ASML. [->span<-] Mechatronics [->span<-] Expand your skillset exponentially. Explore the opportunities in mechatronics at ASML. [->span<-] Optics [->span<-] If you enjoy working at or beyond the edge of what\u2019s possible in optics, then ASML is your ideal environment. [->span<-] Physics [->span<-] Physics is at the heart of everything we do at ASML. Explore our opportunities for physicists. [->span<-] Supporting functions [->span<-] Discover back office jobs and other non-technical opportunities at ASML. [->span<-] Related content [->span<-] / [->span<-] / [->span<-] Manage cookie settings [->span<-] Copyright \u00a9 2019-2026 (ASML) All Rights Reserved"]], ["b", ["[->b<-] "]], ["em", ["[->em<-] "]]], [["p", ["[->p<-] Saved jobs [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Thousands of people work together at ASML to design, manufacture and service the machines in our portfolio, and to keep our internal processes running smoothly. Explore the descriptions and graphics below to find the department that\u2019s your best fit. [->p<-] Our technology in lithography, metrology and inspection is some of the most advanced in the world and our jobs in R&D are at the forefront of this innovation. [->p<-] \u00a0 [->p<-] R&D at ASML is where the sharpest minds in hardware and software come together to challenge each other, learn and grow. We have over 16,000 engineers in R&D with a range of backgrounds including physics, electronics, mechatronics, software, mechanics, data analytics and more. [->p<-] \u00a0 [->p<-] Our R&D colleagues explore what is possible, develop ideas into viable technologies and then industrialize the concepts. [->p<-] Over 7,000 people work around the world at ASML\u2019s cleanroom factory sites. In this high-precision, Lean environment, we assemble, test and deliver our complex lithography and metrology & inspection portfolio, from prototype to final product. [->p<-] ASML has more than 5,000 extremely complex machines in customer fabs around the globe. A machine that\u2019s \u2018down\u2019 can cost customers thousands of euros per minute, so our Customer Support team works hard to keep them running 24 hours a day, 365 days a year. [->p<-] Our Sourcing & Supply Chain colleagues are involved throughout ASML\u2019s entire business, all the way from idea to working product. You\u2019ll find them working around the world finding the right suppliers, making sure our customers have the parts they need in time, and helping to reduce environmental impact and waste [->p<-] You don\u2019t have to be an engineer to enable high-tech. Our colleagues in Finance, Sales & Marketing, HR and other departments make sure our internal processes run with the same speed and accuracy as our lithography machines."]], ["div", ["[->div<-] We saved your job [->div<-] Learn about the technology behind our lithography, metrology and inspection, and software solutions. [->div<-] Find out what it\u2019s like working at a semiconductor industry leader. Discover job benefits, clubs and events, and our culture. [->div<-] Find out how we provide our customers with the hardware, software and services they need to mass produce patterns on silicon."]], ["tr", ["[->tr<-] "]], ["td", ["[->td<-] "]], ["th", ["[->th<-] "]], ["font", ["[->font<-] "]], ["li", ["[->li<-] "]], ["small", ["[->small<-] "]], ["strong", ["[->strong<-] "]], ["h1", ["[->h1<-] Teams"]], ["h2", ["[->h2<-] Search [->h2<-] Learn [->h2<-] Work At ASML [->h2<-] Invest [->h2<-] Get in touch"]], ["h3", ["[->h3<-] Technology [->h3<-] Working at ASML [->h3<-] Products"]], ["h4", ["[->h4<-] R&D [->h4<-] Manufacturing [->h4<-] Customer Support [->h4<-] Sourcing & Supply Chain [->h4<-] Support functions [->h4<-] Social Media"]], ["h5", ["[->h5<-] "]], ["h6", ["[->h6<-] "]], ["span", ["[->span<-] How do you like to work? [->span<-] Choosing a job isn\u2019t just about matching your skills and qualifications. You want a new role to suit the way you like to work. [->span<-] Explore R&D [->span<-] Explore Manufacturing [->span<-] Explore Customer Support [->span<-] Explore Sourcing & Supply Chain [->span<-] Explore support functions [->span<-] Related content [->span<-] / [->span<-] / [->span<-] Manage cookie settings [->span<-] Copyright \u00a9 2019-2026 (ASML) All Rights Reserved"]], ["b", ["[->b<-] "]], ["em", ["[->em<-] "]]], [["p", ["[->p<-] Saved jobs [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Shape your future at ASML. Gain hands-on experience and jumpstart your professional development through our internships, student events and early careers programs. [->p<-] Because our technology is unique and it\u2019s everywhere. In fact, we\u2019re probably part of the electronic device you\u2019re using right now. Working on our pioneering lithography systems will offer you stand-out professional experience and help rapidly develop your skills.\u00a0 [->p<-] Work and learn alongside our engineering experts and help us change the world, one nanometer at a time. Discover roles ranging from software to electrical engineering and join our community of next generation tech leaders. [->p<-] Explore our internships, co-op programs and graduation assignments for students in the Netherlands and the United States. [->p<-] Get support for your future \u2013 see the available scholarships in the Netherlands and the US. [->p<-] Explore our career events and workshops for PhD students and graduates in the Netherlands and the US. [->p<-] Learn about our career events held around the world, where you get to know ASML as an employer. [->p<-] Work AT ASML [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] ASML is headquartered in Veldhoven amid a thriving ecosystem of high-tech companies. Our headquarters is home to more than half of all our employees. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] With 14 customer support sites, two factories, and three R&D centers, our US locations service Intel and other customers and contribute to our holistic product portfolio. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] We have the largest ASML manufacturing site in Asia as well as two training centers, play an essential role in the rapidly growing e-beam market, and work closely with TSMC and major semiconductor fabs. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] Our teams in South Korea work closely with Samsung and other customers and have five locations that include a global distribution center and 4 training centers. [->p<-] Read more [->p<-] We support both global big-name customers and fast-growing local customers with 12 customer support sites, two R&D centers, and one training center. [->p<-] Discover what it\u2019s like to work at ASML. Dive into this interactive section to learn about compensation and benefits, well-being, volunteering and giving back to our communities, employee networks and sports clubs, exciting events, and learning and development. [->p<-] At ASML, we strive to create a safe and inclusive environment for all. We welcome unique voices, identities and experiences, and treat each person with care and respect. [->p<-] Culture & Values [->p<-] Work/life balance [->p<-] Senior Management [->p<-] Compensation and Benefits [->p<-] Career opportunities [->p<-] Diversity & Inclusion"]], ["div", ["[->div<-] We saved your job [->div<-] Thousands of people, one goal [->div<-] With over 60 locations worldwide, we are a growing global force in the semiconductor industry. [->div<-] Discover what your life at ASML could look like, from development, well-being and volunteering to events, clubs and compensation and benefits."]], ["tr", ["[->tr<-] "]], ["td", ["[->td<-] "]], ["th", ["[->th<-] "]], ["font", ["[->font<-] "]], ["li", ["[->li<-] "]], ["small", ["[->small<-] "]], ["strong", ["[->strong<-] "]], ["h1", ["[->h1<-] Students & new graduates"]], ["h2", ["[->h2<-] Search [->h2<-] Enable third party cookies to play this video [->h2<-] ASML's Glassdoor rating [->h2<-] Learn [->h2<-] Work At ASML [->h2<-] Invest [->h2<-] Get in touch"]], ["h3", ["[->h3<-] Why choose ASML to jumpstart your career? [->h3<-] Students and graduates [->h3<-] Our company culture [->h3<-] Interviewing at ASML: Tips and tricks [->h3<-] Teams [->h3<-] ASML at a glance [->h3<-] Life at ASML"]], ["h4", ["[->h4<-] Social Media"]], ["h5", ["[->h5<-] "]], ["h6", ["[->h6<-] New to the interviewing game? We\u2019re here for you. Discover how we conduct interviews at ASML, as well as tips and tricks that will help you make a lasting impression during your interview and set you up for success."]], ["span", ["[->span<-] 01 / 45 [->span<-] Disabled [->span<-] Enabled [->span<-] Internships [->span<-] Scholarships [->span<-] PhD events [->span<-] Career events [->span<-] Choose your location [->span<-] The Netherlands [->span<-] United States [->span<-] Germany [->span<-] Taiwan [->span<-] South Korea [->span<-] Chinese mainland [->span<-] Show me life at ASML [->span<-] Dive into diversity & inclusion [->span<-] 4.1 [->span<-] / [->span<-] 2822 [->span<-] \u00a0 [->span<-] ratings [->span<-] Average score of 4.1 out of 2822 ratings [->span<-] 3.8 [->span<-] 3.8 out of 5 [->span<-] 3.7 [->span<-] 3.7 out of 5 [->span<-] 3.4 [->span<-] 3.4 out of 5 [->span<-] 3.9 [->span<-] 3.9 out of 5 [->span<-] 3.8 [->span<-] 3.8 out of 5 [->span<-] 4.2 [->span<-] 4.2 out of 5 [->span<-] Learn more [->span<-] Related content [->span<-] / [->span<-] / [->span<-] Manage cookie settings [->span<-] Copyright \u00a9 2019-2026 (ASML) All Rights Reserved"]], ["b", ["[->b<-] "]], ["em", ["[->em<-] "]]], [["p", ["[->p<-] Saved jobs [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Back [->p<-] Jumpstart your professional life with our early career programs and make your mark in the semiconductor industry. [->p<-] Our programs will match you to vacancies that are a great fit for your professional experience and educational background. During the selection process, we\u2019ll work with you to consider your skills, ambitions, and interests to identify the best possible position for you. You\u2019ll also get access to a wide selection of learning and development courses and opportunities, so you can also grow within the company.\u00a0 [->p<-] Our programs are designed to help boost your career development within ASML organically. They allow you to participate in an intensive regime that will help you integrate and adjust to ASML\u2019s challenging and fast-paced work environment. Our portfolio is divided into two distinct programs, the ASML Management Traineeships and our Career Gateway Programs. [->p<-] The management traineeship program offers you practical experience in leadership roles and strategic projects. You\u2019ll engage in high-impact assignments from day one. The program offers a steep development path with extensive training in leadership and behavioral competencies, allowing you to quickly enhance your skills. Moreover, through this program you\u2019ll build a strong professional network within ASML by connecting with senior leaders, ASML mentors, and your peers. Most importantly, you\u2019ll also gain insights into the many different sectors of ASML\u2019s business, broadening your understanding of the company's operations and strategic priorities. [->p<-] Through this program you\u2019ll fully immerse yourself in the ASML culture and way of working. You\u2019ll start by working in different positions within ASML and immediately apply the skills and competencies you develop through the program in your day-to-day roles. The program provides immediate opportunities for skill development through training in behavioral competencies and practical application in your roles. Additionally, you\u2019ll be able to connect with colleagues across the company and you\u2019ll be encouraged to join events organized by ASML communities such as Proud, and Atypical, that will help you build a professional network. Lastly, participating in a Gateway program will also get you guidance and support from professional development coaches, sector coordinators, and peer-coaching groups. This will help you navigate your career path better and succeed in your role. [->p<-] Discover what it\u2019s like to work at ASML. Dive into this interactive section to learn about compensation and benefits, well-being, volunteering and giving back to our communities, employee networks and sports clubs, exciting events, and learning and development. [->p<-] At ASML, we strive to create a safe and inclusive environment for all. We welcome unique voices, identities and experiences, and treat each person with care and respect. [->p<-] Culture & Values [->p<-] Work/life balance [->p<-] Senior Management [