| Honoring our technical experts ASML Logo", "Software | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "ASML products & services | Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "EUV lithography systems \u2013 Products | ASML ASML Logo", "DUV lithography systems | Products ASML Logo", "Refurbished systems \u2013 Products | ASML ASML Logo", "Wafer Metrology & inspection systems | Products - ASML ASML Logo", "Computational lithography | ASML ASML Logo", "Customer support | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry 24/7 ASML Logo", "News | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Press releases | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Stories & articles - behind the scenes | ASML ASML Logo", "Share buyback | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Media library | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Media relations contacts | ASML ASML Logo", "Sign up for news alerts | ASML Description ASML Logo", "Investors | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Why invest in ASML | Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Financial strategy | ASML \u2013 Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Capital return and financing | ASML ASML Logo", "Share buyback | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Annual reports | ASML ASML Logo", "Financial results | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Q1 2026 financial results ASML Logo", "Q4 2025 financial results ASML Logo", "Q3 2025 financial results ASML Logo", "Q2 2025 financial results ASML Logo", "Q1 2025 financial results ASML Logo", "Q4 2024 financial results ASML Logo", "Financial overview | ASML ASML Logo", "ASML shares | Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "ASML share price | Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "SEC filings | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Analyst coverage | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Shareholder meetings | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Investor days | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Financial calendar | ASML - Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo", "Contact Investor Relations | ASML ASML Logo", "Contact information | ASML ASML Logo", "SupplierNet - ASML supplier portal | ASML ASML Logo", "CustomerNet - Customer Support portal | ASML ASML Logo", "The machines behind the machines ASML Logo", "ASML 2025 Annual Report  ASML Logo", "Explore your life at ASML | Supplying the semiconductor industry ASML Logo"], "description": ["ASML gives the world's leading chipmakers the power to mass produce patterns on silicon, helping to make computer chips smaller, faster and greener.", "ASML gives the world's leading chipmakers the power to mass produce patterns on silicon, helping to make computer chips smaller, faster and greener.", "", "Get to know ASML, a global company supplying semiconductor manufacturing equipment and the driving innovator behind lithography systems.", "ASML, the world's leading supplier for the semiconductor industry, provides hardware, software and services to chip-makers around the world.", "Get facts and figures about ASML, such as how many employees we have and what makes us the most important tech company you've never heard of.", "Read about who we are, what guides us, and how we strive to make the world better for future generations.", "Learn about the various ASML departments, such as R&D, manufacturing, customer support and corporate functions, that help make us a leader in tech.", "ASML's history is rich with innovation and collaboration. Read our history to learn how we've grown into the semiconductor industry leader we are today.", "ASML has 60 locations across 16 countries and regions worldwide, including the Netherlands, the United States, China, and more.", "We\u2019re committed to transparency. Our shareholders, Supervisory Board and Board of Management all play an important role in ASML\u2019s governance.", "Our executives set and achieve ASML\u2019s objectives, strategy and policies, and manage general affairs.", "Meet our Supervisory Board members, who oversee and advise ASML\u2019s Board of Management.", "We maintain a long-term commitment to our shareholders and value their input during annual meetings", "Read about ASML\u2019s commitment to upholding ethical behavior based on our company values, learn how to report an incident, and download our policies.", "Dynamics in the global semiconductor industry present both opportunities and risks. Learn how risk influences ASML\u2019s strategy.", "KPMG NV has been ASML\u2019s external auditor since reporting year 2016. ASML also has an internal audit department.", "Find and explore ASML\u2019s corporate governance policies and archives.", "ASML sustainability covers every aspect, from corporate citizenship to environmentally friendly practices at every link of the supply chain.", "ASML supports local communities through education, sports, arts and music, and local outreach activities", "We\u2019re fostering science, engineering, technology and math (STEM) education, doing our part to prepare people for the digital future and helping young people reach their potential.", "ASML supports initiatives and organizations that strengthen the culture of a community, including sports partnerships, art festivals and local museums.", "Through ASML\u2019s local outreach activities, we are giving back to our communities across the globe.", "ASML Careers - World's supplier to the semiconductor industry", "Search ASML jobs to start your career in the semiconductor industry! Whether an engineer or researcher, you can help change the future.", "Discover how we conduct interviews at ASML, as well as tips and tricks that will help you make a lasting impression during your interview and set you up for success.", "When working at ASML, you become part of global collaboration. See what it's like to work at ASML, including benefits, training, events and more.", "If you're looking to work in the Netherlands in the high tech-sector, you've found the place: ASML.", "ASML in the US is a diverse R&D and manufacturing powerhouse serving chipmakers such as Intel and contributing to our holistic product portfolio.", "DescriptionIf you want to work with cutting-edge technologies and the semiconductor industry\u2019s finest, you\u2019ll find a place at ASML in Taiwan.", "DescriptionWith a strong focus on customer support and family values, ASML South Korea works with the semiconductor industry\u2019s finest.", "If you\u2019re looking for jobs in China at one of the leading tech companies, look no further than ASML China.", "With our world-leading tech and continued growth, you can advance your career at ASML Japan.", "Our Germany locations, such as Berlin and Dresden, specialize in optical manufacturing technology, precision manufacturing, as well as software development and customer support.", "Explore ASML jobs by category in the semiconductor industry, ranging from data science to human resources and everything in between.", "Research and development, supply chain and sourcing, customer support, manufacturing and support functions: thousands of people work across ASML department teams with one goal.", "Check out our internships, scholarships and career events for students and new graduates globally. ", "Jumpstart your professional life with our early career opportunities. Make your mark while working and learning in a fast-paced, high-tech environment.  ", "Explore our student career opportunities in the Netherlands. Gain hands-on experience by working with a tech industry leader.", "Explore our student career opportunities in the United States. Gain hands-on experience by working with a tech industry leader.", "Explore our student career opportunities in Taiwan. Gain hands-on experience by working with a tech industry leader.", "Learn more about ASML at our campus events, open house days and exhibitions in South Korea.", "Explore our student career opportunities in the Chinese mainland. Gain hands-on experience by working with a tech industry leader.", "Learn about the technology behind ASML lithography systems and other products, used to improve the chip-making process and push the industry forward.", "Learn everything you need to know about how microchips are designed and produced for the semiconductor industry.", "Microchips are the building blocks of technology. Find everything you need to know about the foundations of our digital world.", "Learn all about IC fabrication down to the details. Follow how a microchip is made from the fab to your phone.", "Intel co-founder Gordon Moore\u2019s prediction that the number of transistors on a chip would double every two years has proved to be true since 1965.", "Learn the basics of semiconductor lithography, the critical step in making a microchip.", "In semiconductor lithography, the Rayleigh criterion for resolution determines just how small the transistors on a microchip can be.", "From visible blue light to invisible extreme UV light, ASML\u2019s lithography machines keep innovation in light and lasers moving forward.", "The complex optical systems in ASML\u2019s lithography machines reduce the image to be printed on a wafer to the nanometer level.", "ASML\u2019s lithography machines feature some of the world\u2019s most advanced, precision-engineered mechanical and mechatronic systems.", "ASML systems rely on data from sensors as well as diffraction-based and electron beam measurements to optimize chip production.", "ASML is pushing the fundamental physical concepts about how light interacts with matter to their absolute limit.", "Find out how ASML research and development, a unique collaboration that relies on not only our own innovation but the input of others, works.", "Learn more about the ASML Fellowship Program, an honor program for employees who have made remarkable contributions to the success of ASML.", "Even though you might know of ASML as a hardware company, we actually have one of the world\u2019s largest and most pioneering software communities.", "Explore ASML products and services that optimize the chip-making process, including our advanced lithography machines and metrology tools.", "Providing high resolution in high-volume manufacturing, ASML\u2019s extreme ultraviolet (EUV) lithography systems are pushing Moore\u2019s Law forward.", "ASML's deep ultraviolet (DUV) lithography systems dive deep into the UV spectrum to print the tiny features that form the basis of the microchip.", "ASML refurbishes \u2018classic\u2019 PAS 5500 and TWINSCAN lithography systems for a new life and a new purpose. Contact us today.", "Our optical and e-beam wafer metrology and inspection products quickly and accurately measure pattern quality before and during high-volume chip manufacturing.", "ASML's industry-leading computational lithography products enable accurate lithography simulations that help to improve chip yield and quality.", "Supporting our customers is ASML\u2019s top priority. Our engineers work tirelessly to design customer-centric products and keep them running smoothly.", "Read our latest press releases and announcements to see what's happening at ASML.", "Read through our press releases to learn the latest news and announcements about ASML, including financial results, mergers and acquisitions and more.", "Our stories help bring ASML to life. Let our people and technology inspire you, and read about what we\u2019re doing in our communities.", "", "Download photos of our technology, locations, and more.", "See an overview of ASML's global and regional media relations contacts.", "Receive an email when ASML publishes a new press release, announcement, story, or share buyback update.", "Learn more about investing in ASML, including our financial results, share information, and financial strategy for growth in the semiconductor industry.", "There\u2019s value in being ahead of the curve. Learn how ASML makes technological advances and generate opportunities.", "Read about ASML's long-term financial strategy and growth expectations in the semiconductor industry.", "Read about ASML's dividend and share buyback program, as well as our current outstanding publicly traded bonds, credit ratings and standby facility.", "ASML returns cash to shareholders on a regular basis through share buybacks or capital repayment.", "Read all ASML annual reports, explore our financial results and highlights", "We release annual and quarterly results to ensure investors, both current and potential, are kept informed about our activities.", "View ASML's 2026 first-quarter financial results.", "View ASML's 2025 fourth-quarter and full-year financial results.", "View ASML's 2025 third-quarter financial results.", "View ASML's 2025 second-quarter financial results.", "View ASML's 2025 first-quarter financial results.", "View ASML's 2024 fourth-quarter and full-year financial results.", "View ASML's five-year financial overview, which gives you a look at the financial history of our R&D costs, net profit and more.", "Read about our stock exchange listings and share structure, and see our major shareholders and other important financial information.", "See ASML's share price, both current and historical, on both the Euronext and NASDAQ stock exchanges.", "Find all of ASML's SEC filings, submitted to the US Securities and Exchange Commission.", "View a comprehensive list of sell-side analysts that currently cover ASML.", "Learn about the Annual General Meeting of Shareholders at ASML, including when the meeting convenes and historical shareholder information.", "At our investor days, we keep shareholders, analysts and prospective investors informed about the future of our industry and our role in it.", "Join ASML at one of our many financial events throughout the year, learning more about our place in the industry and how we're growing in it.", "Get in touch with our Investor Relations team to learn more about investing in ASML, whether you're located in Europe, Asia, the US, or anywhere else.", "Get ASML contact information, including general contacts, media, investors, sales and customer support for our headquarters and offices around the globe.", "SupplierNet is the secure ASML supplier portal that features a custom dashboard with information, tools, and more.", "Access training information, documentation, software tools and more at CustomerNet, the secure customer support portal from ASML.", "Discover how ASML is applying AI-native engineering for the next technology era.", "Read the ASML 2025 Annual Report covering strategy, financial results, sustainability performance and leadership messages. ", "Discover what your work-life balance could look like and how we support your well-being. Learn about our networks and clubs and see how our people are supported to develop."], "keywords": ["", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", ""], "language": ["en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", "en", 